  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402350/extras/2d2101a1af696e38b09b04a4403b6aa7.avif?t=1696322041\" width=614 height=165 /></span><br><br>What would you do if once you found yourself in Ancient Greece? <br>Young Emma always knew an answer to this question: she would meet Hercules and join his incredible adventures. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402350/extras/135179b4d9d946edf45d11e13a1d07c9.avif?t=1696322041\" width=614 height=165 /></span><br><br>But how can a common girl from the 21st century help the brave hero? <br>Emma has magic art supplies, and everything she paints becomes real! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402350/extras/2a5f06245a1323796ee6bfd7d993ba3c.avif?t=1696322041\" width=614 height=165 /></span><br><br><br>Does Hercules need a bridge, a ship or dumbbells? <br>All Emma needs is to use her imagination and artist’s talent!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402350/extras/b6439b9b8300070e06bc2cdb6066fa17.avif?t=1696322041\" width=614 height=165 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play 56 thrilling levels<br></li><li> Paint and erase everything you need!<br></li><li> Explore sublevels, bonus levels and super bonus levels.<br></li><li> Easy to learn, hard to master: many ways to complete a level.<br></li><li> Accompany Hercules and Emma during their artistic labour!<br></li><li> Travel through the time to Ancient Greece and back!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402350/extras/15a61279962479de9044425ad1ba0528.avif?t=1696322041\" width=614 height=165 /></span><br><br></li><li> Stunning full HD graphics.<br></li><li> Interactive guide.<br></li><li> Wallpapers.<br></li><li> Additional bonus levels.<br></li><li> Hercules in the 21st century.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402350/extras/cb7884c61067c036c3b34261a1356080.avif?t=1696322041\" width=614 height=165 /></span><br><br><strong>Come and play our latest VR game! </strong><br><br><strong>Come and play our latest VR game! </strong>",
